                    <span>Hopeless. The worst audio book I have in my collection. Nothing like I was expecting.  If you want an book titled Tips For People Who Make Presentations at Seminars or Conferences, this maybe the book for you.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">If you only read one book this year, read this one</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>3</span>
                      /
